  "content": "<h2 id=\"section-ZPRAC_CDS_SIMPLE-key-learning-points\">Key Learning Points</h2>\n<div class=\"text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 text-sm leading-relaxed\"><div class=\"flex items-start gap-2 mb-1.5\"><span class=\"text-brand-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0\">◆</span><span>@AbapCatalog.sqlViewName   → Technical SQL view name visible in SE11</span></div><div class=\"flex items-start gap-2 mb-1.5\"><span class=\"text-brand-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0\">◆</span><span>@AbapCatalog.compiler.compareFilter → Optimizes WHERE clause filtering</span></div><div class=\"flex items-start gap-2 mb-1.5\"><span class=\"text-brand-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0\">◆</span><span>@AbapCatalog.preserveKey   → Preserves key fields as defined</span></div><div class=\"flex items-start gap-2 mb-1.5\"><span class=\"text-brand-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0\">◆</span><span>@AccessControl.authorizationCheck → #CHECK / #NOT_REQUIRED / #NOT_ALLOWED</span></div><div class=\"flex items-start gap-2 mb-1.5\"><span class=\"text-brand-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0\">◆</span><span>@EndUserText.label         → Description text (SE11, ADT)</span></div><div class=\"flex items-start gap-2 mb-1.5\"><span class=\"text-brand-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0\">◆</span><span>@Environment.systemField:#CLIENT → Client field mapping for implicit WHERE</span></div><div class=\"flex items-start gap-2 mb-1.5\"><span class=\"text-brand-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0\">◆</span><span>@Semantics annotations     → Define semantic meaning for fields</span></div><div class=\"flex items-start gap-2 mb-1.5\"><span class=\"text-brand-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0\">◆</span><span>define view { entity_name } → CDS entity name used in ABAP/openSQL</span></div></div>\n<h2 id=\"section-ZPRAC_CDS_SIMPLE-concept-diagram\">Concept Diagram</h2>\n<div class=\"docs-diagram\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 800 500\" font-family=\"'JetBrains Mono', 'Ubuntu', sans-serif\">\n  <defs>\n    <marker id=\"arrow\" viewBox=\"0 0 10 10\" refX=\"9\" refY=\"5\" markerWidth=\"6\" markerHeight=\"6\" orient=\"auto\">\n      <path d=\"M0,0 L10,5 L0,10 Z\" fill=\"#E95420\"/>\n    </marker>\n    <marker id=\"arrow-blue\" viewBox=\"0 0 10 10\" refX=\"9\" refY=\"5\" markerWidth=\"6\" markerHeight=\"6\" orient=\"auto\">\n      <path d=\"M0,0 L10,5 L0,10 Z\" fill=\"#3B82F6\"/>\n    </marker>\n  </defs>\n\n  <!-- Title -->\n  <text x=\"400\" y=\"30\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"16\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#E95420\">CDS View Syntax — Key Elements</text>\n\n  <!-- Annotation block -->\n  <rect x=\"40\" y=\"50\" width=\"720\" height=\"60\" rx=\"6\" fill=\"#FFF3ED\" stroke=\"#E95420\" stroke-width=\"1.5\"/>\n  <text x=\"60\" y=\"72\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"#1e293b\" font-weight=\"bold\">@AbapCatalog.sqlViewName: 'ZPRAC_SQL_SIMPLE'</text>\n  <text x=\"60\" y=\"90\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"#1e293b\" font-weight=\"bold\">@AccessControl.authorizationCheck: #CHECK</text>\n  <text x=\"390\" y=\"72\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#64748b\">── Annotations (metadata declarations)</text>\n\n  <!-- View definition -->\n  <rect x=\"40\" y=\"130\" width=\"720\" height=\"40\" rx=\"6\" fill=\"#E0F2FE\" stroke=\"#3B82F6\" stroke-width=\"1.5\"/>\n  <text x=\"60\" y=\"155\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"#1e293b\" font-weight=\"bold\">define view ZPRAC_CDS_SIMPLE</text>\n  <text x=\"390\" y=\"155\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#64748b\">── View declaration (entity name)</text>\n\n  <!-- SELECT line -->\n  <rect x=\"40\" y=\"190\" width=\"720\" height=\"40\" rx=\"6\" fill=\"#F0FDF4\" stroke=\"#22C55E\" stroke-width=\"1.5\"/>\n  <text x=\"60\" y=\"215\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"#1e293b\" font-weight=\"bold\">  as select from /dmo/travel</text>\n  <text x=\"390\" y=\"215\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#64748b\">── Source entity (CDS view or DB table)</text>\n\n  <!-- Field list -->\n  <rect x=\"40\" y=\"250\" width=\"720\" height=\"180\" rx=\"6\" fill=\"#FEFCE8\" stroke=\"#EAB308\" stroke-width=\"1.5\"/>\n  <text x=\"60\" y=\"275\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"#1e293b\">{</text>\n  <text x=\"80\" y=\"300\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"#1e293b\">  key travel_id    as TravelId,</text>\n  <text x=\"80\" y=\"320\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"#1e293b\">      agency_id    as AgencyId,</text>\n  <text x=\"80\" y=\"340\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"#1e293b\">      customer_id  as CustomerId,</text>\n  <text x=\"80\" y=\"360\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"#1e293b\">      total_price  as TotalPrice,</text>\n  <text x=\"80\" y=\"380\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"#1e293b\">      currency_code as CurrencyCode,</text>\n  <text x=\"80\" y=\"400\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"#1e293b\">      @Semantics.amount.currencyCode: 'CurrencyCode'</text>\n  <text x=\"80\" y=\"420\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"#1e293b\">      booking_fee  as BookingFee</text>\n  <text x=\"60\" y=\"440\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"#1e293b\">}</text>\n  <text x=\"350\" y=\"300\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#64748b\">── Element list with aliases</text>\n  <text x=\"350\" y=\"320\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#64748b\">   key = primary key element</text>\n  <text x=\"350\" y=\"380\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#64748b\">── Field-level annotations</text>\n\n  <!-- Arrow flow -->\n  <line x1=\"220\" y1=\"120\" x2=\"220\" y2=\"135\" stroke=\"#E95420\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" marker-end=\"url(#arrow)\"/>\n  <line x1=\"220\" y1=\"175\" x2=\"220\" y2=\"192\" stroke=\"#E95420\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" marker-end=\"url(#arrow)\"/>\n  <line x1=\"220\" y1=\"235\" x2=\"220\" y2=\"252\" stroke=\"#E95420\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" marker-end=\"url(#arrow)\"/>\n\n  <!-- Flow labels -->\n  <text x=\"200\" y=\"128\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"8\" fill=\"#E95420\">ANNOTATE</text>\n  <text x=\"200\" y=\"183\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"8\" fill=\"#E95420\">DEFINE</text>\n  <text x=\"200\" y=\"245\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"8\" fill=\"#E95420\">SELECT</text>\n</svg></div>\n<h2 id=\"section-ZPRAC_CDS_SIMPLE-cds-source-code\">CDS Source Code</h2>\n<pre><code class=\"language-abap\">@AbapCatalog.sqlViewName: 'ZPRAC_SQL_SIMPLE'\n@AbapCatalog.compiler.compareFilter: true\n@AbapCatalog.preserveKey: true\n@AccessControl.authorizationCheck: #CHECK\n@EndUserText.label: 'Practice CDS - Simple SELECT from /dmo/travel'\ndefine view ZPRAC_CDS_SIMPLE\n  as select from /dmo/travel\n{\n  @Environment.systemField: #CLIENT\n  key client            as Client,\n  key travel_id         as TravelId,\n      agency_id         as AgencyId,\n      customer_id       as CustomerId,\n      @Semantics.date: true\n      begin_date        as BeginDate,\n      @Semantics.date: true\n      end_date          as EndDate,\n      @Semantics.amount.currencyCode: 'CurrencyCode'\n      booking_fee       as BookingFee,\n      @Semantics.amount.currencyCode: 'CurrencyCode'\n      total_price       as TotalPrice,\n      currency_code     as CurrencyCode,\n      description       as Description,\n      status            as Status,\n      @Semantics.user.createdBy: true\n      createdby         as Createdby,\n      @Semantics.date: true\n      createdat         as Createdat,\n      @Semantics.user.lastChangedBy: true\n      lastchangedby     as Lastchangedby,\n      @Semantics.date: true\n      lastchangedat     as Lastchangedat\n}</code></pre>",
